nodes.text: This individual served as the territorial moff of the Arkanis sector during the reign of the Galactic Empire. After releasing a report on Cham Syndulla and the Free Ryloth Movement's Imperial hovertrain attack, Cynabar's InfoNet later reported that someone was making life miserable for the moff, and that on this occasion it wasn't Syndulla before they revealed that the Partisans led by Saw Gerrera had won a number of scores in the sector.
